CHANGELOG for OFFLINEART

Version-Notations without a comment are complete releases, which contains an updated OpenWRT-package and an updated image file.
Versions with "image" is only an updated image file, which can be updated without reinstalling


==== 0.1.3-image  ====

	* Fixed captive Portal detection for iOS7
	* Don't cache redirect-html for not ending up into a browser-loop while visiting a gallery


